# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-06-02 13:12

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:9
translate french dana2_5cfb9131:

    # "It's a fairly normal day of work. I work in Mrs. Mills office all day."
    "C'est une journée de travail assez banale. Je passe toute la journée dans le bureau de Mme Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:10
translate french dana2_85a4b54e:

    # "Cleaning all the normal things."
    "Je m'occupe des tâches habituelles."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:12
translate french dana2_f50e7708:

    # "Typing all normal stuff."
    "Je tape des documents, comme d'habitude."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:13
translate french dana2_d80566b6:

    # "Work passes quickly and I'm busy the entire time."
    "La journée passe vite et je suis occupée tout le temps."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:16
translate french dana2_1dfeab57:

    # bs "Thanks for all your help today, [pcname]. You did good work today."
    bs "Merci pour ton aide aujourd'hui, [pcname]. Tu as bien travaillé."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:17
translate french dana2_e8ce3674:

    # pc "Thank you Mrs. Mills."
    pc "Merci, Mme Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:18
translate french dana2_ed5736f0:

    # bs "I'm going to stay around a little later. You have a good evening."
    bs "Je vais rester un peu plus tard. Passez une bonne soirée."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:19
translate french dana2_dd07e1d2:

    # pc "Okay, you too Mrs. Mills."
    pc "D'accord, vous aussi, Mme Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:20
translate french dana2_fe768c71:

    # "I leave her office and start walking down the hall towards the lobby."
    "Je quitte son bureau et commence à marcher dans le couloir en direction du hall d'entrée."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:25
translate french dana2_e92ba526:

    # "Dana's voice stops me in my tracks. She's arguing with somebody on the phone and sounds upset."
    "La voix de Dana me fait m'arrêter net. Elle se dispute avec quelqu'un au téléphone et a l'air bouleversée."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:26
translate french dana2_1edbfb68:

    # "I don't really mean to eavesdrop, but I also don't want to just walk in on their conversation, so I lean against the wall and wait."
    "Je ne veux pas vraiment écouter, mais je ne veux pas non plus m'immiscer dans leur conversation, alors je m'appuie contre le mur et j'attends."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:27
translate french dana2_506f8528:

    # cw "I'm sorry. I'm just like ten minutes late, but I'm coming home soon, I promise."
    cw "Je suis désolée. J'ai juste dix minutes de retard, mais je rentre bientôt, je te le promets."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:28
translate french dana2_594beb0b:

    # "There is a pause. I can hear a voice on the other side of the phone yelling, but I can't make out the words."
    "Il y a un silence. J'entends une voix à l'autre bout du fil qui crie, mais je ne comprends pas les mots."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:29
translate french dana2_29f965e7:

    # cw "I try to! It's not that easy. I can't just leave my work half-finished."
    cw "J'essaie ! Ce n'est pas si facile. Je ne peux pas laisser mon travail à moitié terminé."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:30
translate french dana2_011812d0:

    # "Her voice drops and catches in her throat."
    "Sa voix s'affaiblit et se brise dans sa gorge."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:31
translate french dana2_3ae30315:

    # voice dana_trying
    # cw "I'm trying. I'm sorry."
    voice dana_trying
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:33
translate french dana2_8788608a:

    # cw "No, I'm not cheating on you. I don't know how many times I have to tell you that."
    cw "Non, je ne te trompe pas. Je ne sais pas combien de fois je vais devoir te le dire."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:34
translate french dana2_d0c4854a:

    # "More yelling comes from the phone receiver."
    "D'autres cris jaillissent du combiné."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:35
translate french dana2_b30f69a4:

    # cw "That's fine. I'll see you tonight then."
    cw "C'est bon. On se voit ce soir alors."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:37
translate french dana2_e7265cb4:

    # "She hangs up the phone and there's a bang as she slams it against the desk."
    "Elle raccroche et on entend un bruit sourd quand elle claque le combiné sur le bureau."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:38
translate french dana2_494fc925:

    # "After a moment, I peek around the corner and see her leaning over with her head buried in her hands, her shoulder shaking as she sobs."
    "Au bout d’un moment, je jette un coup d’œil par-dessus le coin du bureau et je la vois penchée en avant, la tête enfouie dans ses mains, les épaules secouées par les sanglots."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:39
translate french dana2_a3b7daec:

    # "I probably should just stay out of it, but I can't help it."
    "Je devrais probablement rester en dehors de tout ça, mais je ne peux pas m’en empêcher."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:40
translate french dana2_ca8447bf:

    # "I can't stand to see her upset like this. I have this overwhelming urge to fix things."
    "Je ne supporte pas de la voir aussi bouleversée. J’ai cette envie irrésistible d’arranger les choses."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:43
translate french dana2_f041e4b8:

    # "I walk up to her desk and put my hand gently onto her shoulder."
    "Je m’approche de son bureau et pose doucement ma main sur son épaule."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:44
translate french dana2_fa75bbc3:

    # pc "Are you okay?"
    pc "Ça va ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:46
translate french dana2_3619d1fa:

    # "She lifts her head and quickly wipes away her tears."
    "Elle lève la tête et essuie rapidement ses larmes."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:47
translate french dana2_a3f56836:

    # voice dana_justfine
    # cw "Yeah, everything's just fine."
    voice dana_justfine
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:49
translate french dana2_a794c62f:

    # pc "I sort of overheard your conversation."
    pc "J’ai en quelque sorte entendu ta conversation."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:50
translate french dana2_a97815ff:

    # cw "Oh, did you?"
    cw "Ah bon ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:51
translate french dana2_efb33164:

    # "She stays silent for a moment, obviously trying to calm herself down."
    "Elle reste silencieuse un instant, essayant visiblement de se calmer."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:54
translate french dana2_391aa753:

    # "Then suddenly everything seems to burst and she wraps her arms around my waist and buries her face into my stomach."
    "Puis soudain, tout semble éclater et elle enroule ses bras autour de ma taille et enfouit son visage dans mon ventre."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:55
translate french dana2_458c8244:

    # voice dana_sofrustrated
    # cw "I'm sorry, [pcname]. I'm just so frustrated with all of it."
    voice dana_sofrustrated
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:57
translate french dana2_8921cee5:

    # "I put a hand on her back and rub gently as she cries into my shirt."
    "Je pose une main sur son dos et la caresse doucement tandis qu’elle pleure dans ma chemise."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:58
translate french dana2_77fb0dd9:

    # "After a couple minutes of sobbing, she starts to calm down again and she pulls back away from me."
    "Après quelques minutes de sanglots, elle commence à se calmer à nouveau et s’éloigne de moi."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:61
translate french dana2_213acdac:

    # cw "I'm sorry. I got your shirt wet."
    cw "Je suis désolée. J’ai mouillé ta chemise."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:62
translate french dana2_45a788d3:

    # pc "It'll dry. Feeling better now?"
    pc "Ça va sécher. Tu te sens mieux maintenant ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:63
translate french dana2_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "Elle hoche la tête."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:64
translate french dana2_3bb01968:

    # cw "Better. Not great, but better."
    cw "Mieux. Pas génial, mais mieux."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:65
translate french dana2_f02c67f3:

    # cw "I'll figure everything out. I'll get my work done faster and get home earlier, so he won't be mad at me."
    cw "Je vais trouver une solution. Je vais finir mon travail plus vite et rentrer plus tôt, comme ça il ne sera pas fâché contre moi."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:66
translate french dana2_6831ff3c:

    # pc "If you need anybody to talk to, I'm here okay?"
    pc "Si tu as besoin de parler à quelqu’un, je suis là, d’accord ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:67
translate french dana2_0518d8da:

    # cw "Thanks, [pcname]. You're so sweet."
    cw "Merci, [pcname]. Tu es si gentil."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:68
translate french dana2_786b3b21:

    # voice dana_beokay
    # cw "I'll be okay though. I'll see you tomorrow, okay?"
    voice dana_beokay
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:70
translate french dana2_d8858bda:

    # pc "Want me to stay and help with anything?"
    pc "Tu veux que je reste pour t’aider ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:71
translate french dana2_af71dcbc:

    # cw "That's okay. I got it. Thank you though, really."
    cw "C’est bon. Je m’en sors. Mais merci quand même, vraiment."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:72
translate french dana2_859c6cd6:

    # pc "Okay, well I'll see you tomorrow then."
    pc "D’accord, eh bien à demain alors."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:73
translate french dana2_0507fc22:

    # "I give her a final pat on her shoulder before turning and walking outside. I hope she'll be okay. It's a lot to deal with."
    "Je lui donne une dernière petite tape sur l’épaule avant de me retourner et de sortir. J’espère qu’elle s’en sortira. C’est beaucoup à gérer."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:74
translate french dana2_2199c3c0:

    # "I walk through the cool night and get in my car."
    "Je marche dans la fraîcheur de la nuit et je monte dans ma voiture."

translate french strings:

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:2
    old "Dana has been running late getting home from work."
    new "Dana a du retard pour rentrer du travail."

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:3
    old "This scene will happen automatically a few days after the previous scene."
    new "Cette scène se déroulera automatiquement quelques jours après la scène précédente."

